"{\"uid\": \"outsideonline.com-outdoor-adventure-olympics-brooke-raboutou-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"American climber Brooke Raboutou will target both sport climbing events in Paris(Photo: \\tZhe Ji / Getty Images)  Four years ago,Brooke Raboutoubecame thefirst American sport climberto qualify for the discipline's Olympic debut at the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 8, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999966229641083, \"rank\": 2.465128365074445e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 32, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brooke_Raboutou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brooke Raboutou\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brooke_Raboutou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brooke_Raboutou\"}, {\"begin\": 75, \"end\": 80, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995485946893, \"rank\": 4.514053326507151e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 89, \"end\": 92, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gender_neutrality_in_languages_with_gendered_third-person_pronouns\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.098731688225533e-24, \"text\": \"Zhe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gender_neutrality_in_languages_with_gendered_third-person_pronouns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gender_neutrality_in_languages_with_gendered_third-person_pronouns\"}, {\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9996593978344815, \"rank\": 0.0002864620415154394, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}, {\"begin\": 159, \"end\": 167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999966229641083, \"rank\": 2.465128365074445e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Raboutou and 20 other women went head to head in a controversial triple-combined event, vying for a single gold medal based on an aggregate score from three different events: speed, bouldering, and lead.\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While bouldering and lead climbing share some characteristics-a focus on strength and the technical difficulty of climbing movement-speed climbing is a sport all its own, and requires a very different skillset.\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The formatreceived ample criticism.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 700, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Raboutou had a strong showing in bouldering, coming second behind Slovenian Janja Garnbret, who eventually won the gold medal.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia\", \"score\": 0.9969309238966958, \"rank\": 0.0025131210764447356, \"text\": \"Slovenian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia\"}, {\"begin\": 777, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janja_Garnbret\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Janja Garnbret\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janja_Garnbret\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janja_Garnbret\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she struggled in the other two disciplines and eventually finished fifth.\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, Raboutou is back, and she hopes to grab a medal in sport climbing at theParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Theclimbing eventsrun August 5-10.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1034, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Things are different for Raboutou and the other climbers whose sights are set on the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For starters, the International Olympic Committee has dramatically changed the format: speed climbing a stand-alone medal event in Paris.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1262, \"end\": 1267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995485946893, \"rank\": 4.514053326507151e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A second set of medals will be awarded based off of combined scores in the bouldering and lead competitions.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1377, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We spoke with Raboutou about her ambitions in Paris, the atmosphere at the world's biggest stage, and what the new format means for the world's best competitive sport climbers.\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1424, \"end\": 1429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995485946893, \"rank\": 4.514053326507151e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"OUTSIDE: What is your opinion of the new Olympic competition format?I think it's a great change, and I do not know anyone who would argue it is not.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When I competed in Tokyo, it was all three disciplines combined into one.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1724, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.997071888523376, \"rank\": 0.0029366763237731485, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That wasn't only grueling physically, but the way it worked out for scoring wasn't really fair.\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was ranking-based.\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I can say none of us would have chosen to compete in all three events at once.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1983, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The combined format did favor some competitors over others, but in general, Speed is a specialty that deserves its own medals.\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully in the future Boulder and Lead will also be separate and then there will be a Combined event as well.\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2136, \"end\": 2143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulder\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.453053995040336e-21, \"text\": \"Boulder\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But still, those are much more similar disciplines and require similar skills.\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of us competitors do specialize in both of those, but not all three.\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2377, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just think it makes a lot more sense for our sport and gives the opportunity for speed climbers to go to the Olympics and have their own medals.\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some people are still annoyed that Boulder and Lead are combined.\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2560, \"end\": 2567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulder\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.453053995040336e-21, \"text\": \"Boulder\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this is only our second Games, so I am grateful for anything we can get.\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That first split is incredible, and hopefully we can gain more traction and opportunities for more medal sets in the future that will allow more specialization.\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2828, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I honestly do like the combined approach, so I hope we can have both individual and combined in the future.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just trying to take it as it comes and be grateful that we are on this big stage.\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 3027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What did your training look like in the lead up to Paris?I will give you the basics.\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I climb five days a week, usually two days on, one day off, sometimes three days on, one or two days off.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3219, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My training is planned, but it's also adaptable.\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I train with a coach here who I have worked with for four years, Chris Danielson, who's a big part of my growth.\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's a huge mentor to me.\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of the training is on the wall, climbing, but I do strength training as well, weights for power and maintenance.\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3526, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then I do a lot of mental work.\", \"from\": 3527, \"to\": 3562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mental work, like visualization or medication?Both.\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3615, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meditation just for my own well-being, and then visualization-working with sports psychologists and practicing imagery tactics to use throughout training and competition.\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's both visualization of the climbs, but also different cues to help get me in the present moment, focused on myself, and in a good mental place.\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How does the atmosphere of the Olympics differ from that at major climbing events like the World Cup?I remember having a moment of realization at the Games because it did feel so different in some ways.\", \"from\": 3938, \"to\": 4140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LikeThis is crazy.\", \"from\": 4141, \"to\": 4159, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is climbing's first Olympics, and there are only 20 of us on the mat.So I had that realization, but still, we are just climbing.\", \"from\": 4160, \"to\": 4293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the same game that we get to do every day, at all the other competitions.\", \"from\": 4294, \"to\": 4375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's more a perception change than an actual change, which to me is helpful.\", \"from\": 4377, \"to\": 4453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I like to look at it that way.\", \"from\": 4454, \"to\": 4484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's an exciting opportunity, how big this is, but at the end of the day, nothing has changed.\", \"from\": 4485, \"to\": 4579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are still doing what we love out there on the mats.\", \"from\": 4580, \"to\": 4634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I do not know.\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I would say yes and no.\", \"from\": 4653, \"to\": 4676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is different for sure, but a lot of that is just perception as well, and attention toward our sport, less real internal change or physical change.\", \"from\": 4677, \"to\": 4826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What draws you to competitive climbing?I love climbing just for itself, for the movement.\", \"from\": 4828, \"to\": 4917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's something that drives me and I am impassioned by, and I find that both indoors and outdoors.\", \"from\": 4918, \"to\": 5017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I have really fallen in love with competition for the mental growth that it takes.\", \"from\": 5018, \"to\": 5104, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Learning about myself through competition, through challenges, through success, it's been really eye-opening and purposeful for me.\", \"from\": 5105, \"to\": 5236, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To be a high-level competitor and get to experience this world and those extremes, and have that time for myself to reflect on how I show up.\", \"from\": 5238, \"to\": 5379, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have learned so much through competition climbing about my own development.\", \"from\": 5380, \"to\": 5457, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's something I am really grateful for and love on a bigger picture perspective.\", \"from\": 5458, \"to\": 5541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Internally, I love the movement of climbing, and I love the feelings it gives me and the confidence it gives me in the way I am able to express myself.\", \"from\": 5542, \"to\": 5693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This interview was edited for space and clarity.\", \"from\": 5695, \"to\": 5743, \"entities\": []}]}"